name: v0.22.0
body:
**Bidict is the bidirectional mapping library for Python.**
_If you or your organization depends on bidict, please consider [sponsoring bidict on GitHub](https://github.com/sponsors/jab)._

Please see https://bidict.readthedocs.io/en/v0.22.0/changelog.html for the notable changes in this release.
